English: Well, if I want to convert two radians, again, I have degrees, so I've got to divide by degrees
or put the degrees on the bottom to cancel out.
Degrees will cancel with degrees, and I'm left with radians on top.
Chinese: 嗯，如果我想将两弧度转换为度数，我已有度数，因此必须用度数去除或将其置于分母以约去。
度数会与度数相互抵消，最后结果只剩下弧度在分子位置。
度数会与度数相消，而我剩下的就是分子上的弧度。

input: Well, if I want to convert two radians, again, I have degrees, so I've got to divide by degrees, or put the degrees on the bottom to cancel out. Degrees will cancel with degrees, and I'm left with radians on top.
